      • getLectureHash

        public final java.lang.String getLectureHash()
        Calculate the hash for this lecture. The hash used on both the client application and the backend server is the combined hash of: 1. The UNIX timestamp string of the start time of the lecture 2. The UNIX timestamp string of the end time of the lecture 3. The course name as it appears on TimeEdit 4. The HiG code of the course 5. The room as it appears on TimeEdit 6. The lecturer as it appears on TimeEdit
        Returns:
        SHA-1 of the LectureItem's uniquely identifying values.
